text: Daphne and the Pirate is a 1916 American silent adventure drama movie directed by Christy Cabanne and starring Lillian Gish, Elliott Dexter, Walter Long, Howard Gaye, Lucille Young, Richard Cummings, Jack Cosgrave, Joseph Singleton, George C. Pearce, W. E. Lawrence, Pearl Elmore, Jewel Carmen. It was distributed by Triangle Film Corporation. == Other websites == * Category:1916 drama movies Category:1910s adventure movies Category:American adventure movies Category:American drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:Movies directed by Christy Cabanne
